IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. CALLER.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 AMT PIC 9(5) VALUE 1500.
01 STAT PIC 9(3) VALUE 0.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PROC.
    CALL "PAYROLL" USING AMT, STAT.
    DISPLAY STAT.
    MOVE 500 TO AMT.
    CALL "PAYROLL" USING AMT, STAT.
    DISPLAY STAT.
    STOP RUN.

IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL.
DATA DIVISION.
LINKAGE SECTION.
01 IN-AMT PIC 9(5).
01 OUT-STAT PIC 9(3).
PROCEDURE DIVISION USING IN-AMT, OUT-STAT.
    IF IN-AMT > 1000 THEN
        MOVE 1 TO OUT-STAT
    ELSE
        MOVE 0 TO OUT-STAT
    END-IF.
    EXIT PROGRAM.
